0.50.1
     * you can select background color: 'decurs RoyalBlue1'. Note that it
       _DOES NOT_ affect color of cursor. use gcolorsel or xcolorsel to look
       for good colors.

0.50.0
     * There is now cursor -selection window. Press 'Sel'.
     * made glyph drawing more modular.
     * fixed repainting bugs.
     * fixed couple segfaults. (unlikely to happen.. but ohwell)
     * Early support for pixmaps in toolbar.
     * indentation madness. emacs at defaults sucks.

0.42.2
      * bugfix for right mouseclick
      * help-box for keys
      * command-line simpolifications for compiling.
0.42.1-alpha
